 fabric from rural villages in Turkey, India and Nepal.<a href=&quot;#fn60\&quot; id=\"ref60\">60<\/a><br \/>\nSamples of Farr&rsquo;s abstract designs below include one recalling Rothko&rsquo;s bold rectangular forms and another, Franz Kline&rsquo;s spirited strokes.<br \/>\n<br \/>\n<br \/>\n<br \/>\n57. Dinah Hall, &ldquo;Inside the rug designer Christopher Farr&rsquo;s colourful Californian home, <em>The Telegraph<\/em>, accessed 07\/03\/2015, http:\/\/www.telegraph.co.uk\/lifestyle\/interiors\/11301590\/Inside-the-rug-designer-Christopher-Farrs-colourful-Californian-home.html <a href=&quot;#ref57\&quot; title=\"Jump back to footnote 57 in the text.\">\u21a9<\/a><br \/>\n58. Ibid.<a href=&quot;#ref58\&quot; title=\"Jump back to footnote 58 in the text.\">\u21a9<\/a><br \/>\n59. <em>Christopherfarr.com<\/em>, accessed 07\/03\/2015, http:\/\/christopherfarr.com\/history<a href=&quot;#ref60\&quot; title=\"Jump back to footnote 60 in the text.\">\u21a9<\/a><br \/>\n60.  &ldquo;Q&amp;A With Christopher Farr,&rdquo; <em>Dwell<\/em>, accessed 07\/03\/2015, http:\/\/www.dwell.com\/interviews\/article\/q-christopher-farr<a href=&quot;#ref60\&quot; title=\"Jump back to footnote 60 in the text.\">\u21a9<\/a>","resource_full_text":"","resource_types_for_resource_id":"Archival Material","resource_asset_type":"10","resource_image_thumbnail":"..\/images\/Rsrc_TN_003557.jpg","resource_asset_type_label":"","resource_file_size":"0.0 kB","resource_file_size_unformatted":"118.8076171875","resource_grade_level":"","resource_curriculum":"","resource_tour":"","resource_file_time":"00m 00s","resource_file_time_unformatted":"0","resource_source_detail":"\"Tools of the Trade: 19th- and 20th-Century Architectural Trade Catalogs,\" Case 8, Ryerson &amp; Burnham Libraries, August 4, 2015-October 12, 2015.<br \/>\n<br \/>\n<a href=&quot;https:\/\/digital-libraries.artic.edu\/cdm\/ref\/collection\/mqc\/id\/68831&quot;>Link to R&amp;B Archives Digital Collections record<\/a><br \/>\n<br \/>\n<